Updates to X.509 Policy Validation
2024", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This document updates RFC 5280 to replace the algorithm for X.509 policy validation with an equivalent, more efficient algorithm.  The original algorithm built a structure that scaled exponentially in the worst case, leaving implementations vulnerable to denial-of-service attacks."]; 

